name: Yane
Lore: 'The youngest handmaiden, Yane stayed behind on Naboo while Amidala pleaded her case to the Galactic Senate. Musician.',
Text: 'While at a Theed Palace site or same site as Amidala, opponent''s Republic characters are deploy +1 here and Yane is forfeit +3. If just lost during a battle, may use 2 Force to place Yane in Used Pile.',
